videos.description: Dwyane Wade is greeted by the Duke home crowd as he catches the Blue Devils vs. Wake Forest.
videos.headline: Wade makes appearance at Duke game

videos.description: Marques Bolden gets a big and-1 on a putback of Tre Jones' layup.
videos.headline: Bolden gets big and-1 on putback

videos.description: Jack White is on fire in the first half, hitting back-to-back 3-pointers for the Blue Devils.
videos.headline: White hits back-to-back 3s to get crowd amped

videos.description: Sharone Wright Jr. hits a big 3-pointer for Wake Forest as they go up by 10 vs. No. 4 Duke on the road.
videos.headline: Wake Forest stays hot from 3-point range

videos.description: Alex O'Connell hits a big and-1 on his way to a 3-point play to tie the game for the Blue Devils.
videos.headline: O'Connell hits big and-1

videos.description: R.J. Barrett comes up with the clutch and-1 with just over a minute to go in the game.
videos.headline: Barrett has ice in his veins

videos.description: Wake Forest misses a three and comes up just short on the layup as they fall to Duke 71-70 on the road.
videos.headline: Wake Forest misses two opportunities for win
